Because sometime, you just need a little bit of punk with your coding.

tuRbonegro

Spoiler: this package was designed just for fun ;)

tuRbonegro_hex

This packages contains only one function, which launch and plays a random Turbonegro clip in your R Viewer.

This function has three parameters:

  • @param width width of the video, in pixel. Default is 560.
  • @param height width of the video, in pixel. Default is 315.
  • @param autoplay set video autoplay. Default is TRUE.

Install

To install on your machine :

devtools::install_github("ColinFay/tuRbonegro")

Play a random clip

library(tuRbonegro)
tuRbonegro()
